    • Method Detail

      • onDataUpdateDone

        void onDataUpdateDone(DataUpdateStatus status,
                      java.util.List<BlukiiAction> syncedActions,
                      java.util.List<BlukiiAction> errorActions)
        Is called when asynchronous function Blukii.updateData(DataUpdateListener) is finished.

        It returns the update success or error status and a list of updated BlukiiActions and errors.

        Parameters:
        status - success or error state
        syncedActions - list of write actions (BlukiiAction) the has been successfully called to blukii device
        errorActions - list of error actions (BlukiiAction)
